Organization: Northwestern University, Evanston Illinois.
Date: Thu, 6 Aug 1992 18:54:16 GMT
Lines: 666

Hi everyone!

This is Game 5, which means we've reached the half-point.  That's worth
celebrating, isn't it? :)  Therefore, this game should be dedicated to
someone special, like someone that everyone on IGS would like to thank.
Okay, this time, this "someone" is *tim*, who has been the "Keeper of the
Server." 

Thanks, tim!!

And personally, I have this special memory of being kicked out once from
the Server by tim. :-)

jzy, NR ^_^

